AI-Powered Excel Mock Interviewer - PoC
======================================

Structure:
- backend/app.py        -> FastAPI backend (sessions, questions, evaluation)
- backend/db_init.py    -> Simple SQLite initialization (creates tables + seeds 20 questions)
- frontend/streamlit_app.py -> Streamlit UI for candidate to take interview, upload spreadsheets, and download PDF report
- requirements.txt      -> Python dependencies

Notes:
- LLM integration uses groqapi. Set environment variable groq_API_KEY before running the backend.
  Example: export OPENAI_API_KEY=\"sk-...\" (Linux/Mac) or set in Windows env vars.

Run locally:
1) Start backend:
   uvicorn backend.app:app --reload --port 8000
2) Start frontend:
   streamlit run frontend/streamlit_app.py --server.port 8501

The PoC uses:
- Rule-based checks for formula questions
- GROQAPI scoring for explanation questions (if GROQ_API_KEY provided)
- Spreadsheet upload evaluation (basic checks using pandas/openpyxl)
- PDF report generation using ReportLab

